{
  "stem": "24171.5",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The night-- the day shift-- the night shift has to go to work, and the day shift comes in.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There is, you know, in that time they gave the-- the [? soups ?] out.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So they called me in to help out, to take out those potatoes from-- from the things.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And my nieces were sleeping, still, at that time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Do you know what I did?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was throwing potatoes in my bosom.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had a little [INAUDIBLE] in here, and throw [INAUDIBLE] potatoes were hot, you know?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was not allowed to go to their barracks because they were sleeping.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I-- I took a lot of risk, all the time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- and I put, you know, it in, in there, whatever there was.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had a little apron, which I didn't need it, kind of, to use it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I wrapped those potatoes, and put for them to their feet.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It warmed them while they were sleeping, and it warmed them when they got up.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And on top of that, they were those cans-- you know, from-- from some certain thing in the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I made two holes, with a piece of string.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And while, as I say, I had been kind of close to the kitchen, so I ate more than other ones.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So my soup, I could give them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They went to work, and they had what to eat there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That's what she writes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I wish you could read that Hungarian letter.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so things like that, it was there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And another thing-- like, I had my shoes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the little one, I don't remembered.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They fell apart, the shoes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she was wearing these Holland shoes-- you know, the wooden ones?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the snow, you know.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
